{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c9524fcf1d","title":"周恩来关于制止北京外语学院武斗的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a85bb53b06","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":14,"articleId":"c9524fcf1d"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f99e316e2c","type":"title","text":"周恩来关于制止北京外语学院武斗的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d"},{"id":"c0b40f63b6","type":"paragraph","text":"〖十四日晚，在毛主席、林付主席以及中央其它领导同志接见解放军代表时，周总理对崇碧同志的指示。11月15日上午李钟奇同志在外院传达。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d"},{"id":"81cd5c322e","type":"paragraph","text":"一、外语学院昨天发生的这场大规模武斗，为什么这股武斗风总是煞不住？要检查形成这次武斗的原因，追究责任。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d"},{"id":"8c8ea0b838","type":"paragraph","text":"二、外语学院二派都犯过这样那样的错误。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d"},{"id":"aa607cbb00","type":"paragraph","text":"三、这些问题的解决靠武斗是不行的，只能通过摆事实，讲道理来解决。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d"}],"page":{"id":"81b4d75411","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c9524fcf1d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}